{"tid":1242141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主派在立法會大會默哀悼念身故示威者","createTime":"2019-06-19T03:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T05:57:16.000Z","uid":20933,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"100b04f7fea5fd1b464474cfcfae42f3fab2f6b3","tid":1242141,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:01:41.000Z","msg":"停開一個星期的立法會在早上11時召開大會，多名民主派議員身穿黑色衣服，手持白色鮮花，表示要默哀一分鐘，悼念在金鐘太古廣場墮樓身亡的反修例示威者。<br />\n<br />\n連日來未有公開發言的保安局長李家超亦有出席，回應民主派議員質疑警方濫用武力的急切質詢。<br />\n<br />\n完成腦部手術申請休假的公民黨陳淑莊，亦有出席會議。"},{"pid":"6a5c10cb28b8eebfc81f994954376bbf1f15e86f","tid":1242141,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:02:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1125453&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1125453%26csid%3D261_341&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=a12a44e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1125453&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"8aca36c758d39edea731e2c4052435175f72b2e9","tid":1242141,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/QxrPX0G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxrPX0G.jpg&h=96100a0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d84e07942e49b0670e8cfdd717d03c34878696d8","tid":1242141,"uid":252182,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:48:18.000Z","msg":"呢個要 support ; 寫入歷史嘅文獻之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a87a115ee9046a2c18ffb7f3916f1f4a42563ef","tid":1242141,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"佢地做呢樣野